<plot>And old man tells a story to his niece about a drunk, Giulio, who meets a strange man, Mattia, on a deserted beach. Mattia, though he's Italian, wants to speak English because he is waiting for his future wife, a teacher from New York, whom he is never met before. The unlikely pair slowly become friends and this meeting will change their their lives in ways they had not anticipated.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?178805</url></doc>
